Definition: an underground banking system based on trust whereby money can be made available internationally without actually moving it or leaving a record of the transaction
Example: terrorists make extensive use of hawala
Synonyms: banking_industry, noun, act, terrorism, c, an, underground, banking, system, based, on, trust, whereby, money, can, be, made, available, internationally, without, actually, moving, it, or, leaving, a, record, of, the, transaction, terrorists, make, extensive, use
Category: noun.group
